  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK491">
<l>toṭaṅkaṟka vevviṉaiyu meḷḷaṟka muṟṟu </l>
<l>miṭaṅkaṇṭa piṉṉal latu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let not (a king) despise (an enemy), nor undertake any thing (against him), until he has obtained (a suitable) place for besieging him.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
